trans-unit.source: Provides a collection container that enables ASP.NET server controls to maintain a list of their child controls.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en samling beholder som gjør det mulig for ASP.NET serverkontroller å beholde en liste over de underordnede-kontrollene.

trans-unit.source: You can access any of the properties and methods of the ControlCollection class through the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Du har tilgang til egenskaper og metoder for klassen ControlCollection via den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A?displayProperty=fullName>egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.Controls%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: Since the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control> class is the base class for all ASP.NET server controls, all server controls inherit this property.
trans-unit.target: Siden det <xref:System.Web.UI.Control>klassen er basisklasse for alle serverkontroller for ASP.NET, arver alle serverkontroller denne egenskapen.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control>

trans-unit.source: For more information about collections, see [Collections and Data Structures](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om samlinger, se [samlinger og datastrukturer](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> class for the specified parent server control.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> serverkontroll angitte overordnede klasse.

trans-unit.source: The ASP.NET server control that the control collection is created for.
trans-unit.target: ASP.NET serverkontroll som samlingen for kontrollen som er opprettet for.

trans-unit.source: Occurs if the owner parameter is .
trans-unit.target: Oppstår hvis den owner parameteren er .

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Legger til den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> objektet i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The new control is added to the end of an ordinal index array.
trans-unit.target: Den nye kontrollen legges til slutten av en ordensindeksen matrise.

trans-unit.source: The control can be an instance of any ASP.NET server control, a custom server control you create, or a literal control.
trans-unit.target: Kontrollen kan være en forekomst av en ASP.NET-serverkontroll, en egendefinert serverkontroll du oppretter eller en litteral kontroll.

trans-unit.source: To add a control to the collection at a specific index location, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.AddAt%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil legge til en kontroll i innsamlingen på en bestemt indeksplassering, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.AddAt%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.AddAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> å legge til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Thrown if the child parameter does not specify a control.
trans-unit.target: Et hvis den child parameteren angir ikke en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: Thrown if the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Et hvis den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> er skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> object to the collection at the specified index location.
trans-unit.target: Legger til den angitte <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> objektet i samlingen ved plasseringen angitt indeks.

trans-unit.source: The added control can be an instance of any ASP.NET server control, a custom server control you create, or a literal control.
trans-unit.target: La til kontrollen kan være en forekomst av en ASP.NET-serverkontroll, en egendefinert serverkontroll du oppretter eller en litteral kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The location in the array at which to add the child control.
trans-unit.target: Plasseringen i matrisen som du vil legge til underordnede kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> å legge til i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: The child parameter does not specify a control.
trans-unit.target: Den child parameteren angir ikke en kontroll.

trans-unit.source: The index parameter is less than zero or greater than the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName> property.
trans-unit.target: Den index parameteren er mindre enn null eller større enn den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName> egenskapen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> er skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: Removes all controls from the current server control's <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Fjerner alle kontroller fra den gjeldende serverkontroll <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to empty a custom control's <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection> when you override the <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.CreateChildControls%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.DataBind%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden tømme en egendefinert kontroll <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection>Når du overstyre den <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.CreateChildControls%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Web.UI.Control.DataBind%2A>metoder.</xref:System.Web.UI.Control.DataBind%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.Control.CreateChildControls%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection>

trans-unit.source: Do this when you develop composite, templated controls or templated data-bound controls.
trans-unit.target: Gjøre dette når du utvikler sammensatt, organisasjonsapper kontroller eller organisasjonsapper databindingselementer-kontroller.

trans-unit.source: Determines whether the specified server control is in the parent server control's <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Bestemmer om den angitte serverkontrollen er i den overordnede serverkontroll <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The server control to search for in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Serverkontroll til å søke etter i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the specified server control exists in the collection; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis den angitte serverkontrollen finnes i samlingen. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Copies the child controls stored in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object to an <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> object, beginning at the specified index location in the <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Kopier de underordnede kontrollene som er lagret i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objekt en <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> objektet Start fra den angitte indeksplasseringen i den <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> to copy the child controls to.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.Array?displayProperty=fullName> å kopiere underordnede kontroller til.

trans-unit.source: The zero-based relative index in `array` where copying begins.
trans-unit.target: Den nullbaserte indeksen for relativ i `array` der kopiering begynner.

trans-unit.source: array is not and not one-dimensional.
trans-unit.target: arrayer ikke og ikke endimensjonal.

trans-unit.source: Gets the number of server controls in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object for the specified ASP.NET server control.
trans-unit.target: Henter antall serverkontroller i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objekt for den angitte ASP.NET serverkontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The number of server controls in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Antall serverkontroller i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves an enumerator that can iterate through the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter en opplisting som kan gå gjennom den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The enumerator to iterate through the collection.
trans-unit.target: Opplistingen for å gå gjennom samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Retrieves the index of a specified <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> object in the collection.
trans-unit.target: Henter indeksen for et angitt <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> objektet i samlingen.

trans-unit.source: Use this method to determine the index location of the specified server control in the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection> object.
trans-unit.target: Bruk denne metoden til å fastslå indeksplasseringen for den angitte serverkontrollen i den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection>objektet.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"></xref> for which the index is returned.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Control"> </xref> for indeksen returneres.

trans-unit.source: The index of the specified server control.
trans-unit.target: Indeksen for den angitte serverkontrollen.

trans-unit.source: If the server control is not currently a member of the collection, it returns -1.
trans-unit.target: Hvis serverkontrollen ikke er medlem av samlingen, returneres -1.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object is read-only.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objektet er skrivebeskyttet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the control is read-only; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis kontrollen er skrivebeskyttet. Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Standard <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object is synchronized.
trans-unit.target: Henter en verdi som angir om den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objekt er synkronisert.

trans-unit.source: This property is always <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen er alltid <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reference to the server control at the specified index location in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref> object.
trans-unit.target: Henter en referanse til serverkontroll på den angitte indeksplasseringen i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: The location of the server control in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Plasseringen av serverkontroll i den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The reference to the control.
trans-unit.target: Referansen til kontrollen.

trans-unit.source: The index parameter is less than zero or greater than or equal to <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Den index parameteren er mindre enn null eller større enn eller lik <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.Count%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.

trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil fjerne en kontroll fra en indekseringsplassering, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.RemoveAt%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.RemoveAt%2A>

trans-unit.source: The server control to be removed.
trans-unit.target: Serverkontroll som skal fjernes.

trans-unit.target: Fjerner en underordnet kontroll på den angitte indeksplasseringen fra den <xref href="System.Web.UI.ControlCollection"> </xref> objektet.

trans-unit.source: To remove a control from the collection based on its value, use the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.Remove%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil fjerne en kontroll fra samlingen basert på verdien, kan du bruke den <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.Remove%2A>metoden.</xref:System.Web.UI.ControlCollection.Remove%2A>

trans-unit.source: The ordinal index of the server control to be removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: Ordensindeksen serverkontroll som skal fjernes fra samlingen.
